# Coffee Machine Simulator â˜•

A simple terminal-based coffee machine simulator. It allows users to select a type of coffee, checks if enough resources are available, processes the "payment," and updates the inventory.

## Features
- Coffee types: espresso, latte, cappuccino
- Resource tracking (water, milk, coffee)
- Simulated coin input and transaction validation
- Refill and report options for admin mode

## Technologies
- Python

## What I learned
- Building menu-driven interfaces
- Using dictionaries to store and manage data
- Input validation and basic state management

## Run the program
```bash
python coffee_machine.py
